# ER-Archipelago superrepo .gitignore
# The forks are SUBMODULES (tracked by gitlink, not by content here): the 6 4laric forks
# plus your Paramdex and yet-another-tab-control forks. Everything below is NOT committed.

# --- non-repo vendored / large dirs ---
# Contains the copyrighted game exe + vanilla param dumps. NEVER commit (licensing).
/elden_ring_artifacts/
# AP generation test output.
/gen-test/
# Downloaded Nexus randomizer package.
/Elden Ring Randomizer-428-v0-11-4-1763103112 (2)/

# --- generated / build outputs ---
# packaged apworld (rebuilt by build.ps1) -- comment on its own line; inline # breaks the pattern
eldenring.apworld
eldenring_*.apworld
gensweep*
# bake output (slot/seed/location_flags)
apconfig.json
preflight_*.log
*.log
# per-gen compact diagnostic (dlcdiag.py output; raw .log already ignored)
gendiag_*.txt

# --- backups / archives ---
*.bak
*.tar.gz

# --- python cache (poptracker generator) ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# --- OS / editor
# --- boss-attribution dry-run analysis outputs (regenerate via boss_attribution_dryrun.py / tune_complement.py) ---
boss-attribution-dryrun.csv
check-nearest-grace.csv
smithing_stone_distribution.csv

# --- tagged editor backups (the *.bak rule above misses *.bak_<tag>) ---
*.bak_*

# --- diag dumps (apworld gen / sphere-tier) ---
ER_DIAG.txt
ER_SPHERE_TIERS_*.txt

# --- Rust build output (rust-client-spike / fswap-er-client-pr crates) ---
target/


# --- AP run logs / probe temp (were committed before these rules existed) ---
ap_bake_*.log
ap_error_*.txt
ap-client-log.txt
_dg_tmp.py
.write_test_xyz

# --- seed-parking: keep metadata (.ps1/.txt/.yaml/.md), NEVER the deployed game blobs ---
# game-files/ = provisioned map/event/msg/script .dcx + regulation.bin (copyrighted, generated).
# save/ = ER0000.sl2 personal saves. mods/ = compiled archipelago.dll. ap-server/ = AP_*.zip output.
# _pre-restore-backup-*/ = full duplicate snapshot of all of the above.
seeds-archive/*/game-files/
seeds-archive/*/save/
seeds-archive/*/mods/
seeds-archive/*/ap-server/
seeds-archive/**/_pre-restore-backup-*/
# Save files are never source, anywhere in the tree.
*.sl2

# --- vendored / scratch dirs that must NOT be committed to the superrepo ---
# Vanilla game data dump (copyrighted; same rule as /elden_ring_artifacts/). NEVER commit.
/vanilla-game-snapshot/
# PR-prep scratch (duplicate source copies + draft bodies/plans).
/fswap-er-client-pr/
# Third-party Seamless Co-op mod config.
/seamless-coop/
# SoulsFormatsNEXT CI scratch (build.yml + PR helper).
/soulsformatsnext-ci/
